<plot>Young artist-turned-detective Kevin Tomlin takes on a standard homicide case. But Kevin starts doubting his special talent to solve cases by drawing the crime scenes when a number of other distracting clues arise. Kevin must decide what is best for this case: following his drawing talent, or these ambiguous clues. Kevin's insecurities lead him to try following both paths and this inability to make a decision ultimately gets him in over his head.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?267757</url></doc>
